<view class="page"><view class="nav" style="padding-top:{{navTop}}px;height:{{navHeight}}px"><view bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}"/><text>返回课包管理</text></view></view><scroll-view class="scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height:{{navSpacer}}px"></view><view class="content"><text class="title">课包详情</text>
  <view class="hero"><image src="{{cover}}" mode="aspectFill"/><view><text>{{packageInfo.name}}</text><text>{{packageInfo.status}}</text><text>{{packageInfo.classInfo}}</text></view><text>{{packageInfo.price}}</text></view>
  <view class="summary"><view><text>课时</text><text>{{packageInfo.hours}}</text></view><view><text>有效期</text><text>{{packageInfo.valid}}</text></view><view><text>已购学员</text><text>{{packageInfo.buyers}}</text></view></view>
  <view class="panel"><view class="section-title">课消规则</view><view class="rules"><view><text>正常课消</text><text>按课时扣减，课消后剩余课时自动更新。</text></view><view><text>赠课规则</text><text>赠送课时优先消耗，不与有效期叠加。</text></view><view><text>请假补课</text><text>请假需提前24小时申请，按规则安排补课。</text></view><view><text>过期处理</text><text>课包到期未使用课时将自动失效。</text></view></view></view>
  <view class="panel"><view class="section-title">最近购买记录</view><view class="purchase" wx:for="{{purchases}}" wx:key="name"><image src="{{item.avatar}}" mode="aspectFill"/><view><text>{{item.name}}</text><text>{{item.date}}</text></view><view><text>{{item.price}}</text><text>到期 {{item.expires}}</text></view></view></view>
  <view class="panel"><view class="section-title">管理操作</view><view class="manage"><view bindtap="edit"><text>编</text><view><text>编辑基础信息</text><text>修改课包名称、价格等</text></view></view><view bindtap="changeStatus"><text>架</text><view><text>上下架</text><text>控制前台展示状态</text></view></view><view bindtap="showStudents"><text>人</text><view><text>查看学员</text><text>查看购买与在学学员</text></view></view></view></view>
  <view class="pc-tip">复杂售价方案请前往PC端课包管理</view><view class="safe"></view>
</view></scroll-view></view>
